Adherents of Christianity

"Christian" redirects here. For other uses, see [Christian (disambiguation)](/Christian_(disambiguation)).

Christians
The image depicts [Jesus](/Jesus) calling his disciples to become "[fishers of men](/Fishers_of_men)" after the [miraculous catch of fish](/Miraculous_catch_of_fish), as interpreted by [Raphael](/Raphael) around 1515.

